These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, jazz, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, russian, spanish, turkish
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, fanta, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the colombian is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person drinking tea is the russian##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the colombian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the fan of blues##7
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country | jazz    | blues   |
| Nationality   | colombian | spanish | russian | turkish |
| Beverage           | milk       | fanta   | tea  | soy-milk     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

