There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, russian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is the polish##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 5. the german is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the russian is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
