.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer, project-manager, scientist
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, february, june
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the scientist is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the project-manager##1
 8. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the police-officer is the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the mechanic is not the person who's birthday is in november##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk       | mirinda         | sprite       |
| Hobby         | cooking     | video-games    | rock-climbing   | magic-tricks |
| Job           | scientist   | police-officer | project-manager | mechanic     |
| Birthday   | june      | november          | may           | february |

