 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 8. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating tomato##7
10. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
12. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
