 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the french##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess      | cooking   | sudoku   | puzzles       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| City         | berlin   | prague    | san-francisco   | liverpool |

