.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, classical, gospel, rock
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, drawing, hiking, reading
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 5. the fan of classical is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of rock##7
 8. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of gospel##1
12. the fan of gospel is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
